Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個地方  有個夢境之門打開了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你與蒼星石之間  發生了什麼事對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石好可憐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石打開夢境之門也不是什麼奇怪的事的說  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來事有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出現在翠星石面前  究竟是在打什麼鬼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,n之領域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不用插手管這件事的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我與蒼星石之間的問題的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能給大家添麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前明明給我們添了那麼多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你說這種話還真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來這一套  噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉…閉嘴的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純的意思是要你這次也來給我們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟純是我真紅的僕從
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你說過了他為人不壞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法  那你們就快點跟過來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙嘴巴還是一樣壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}「柵欄」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我第一次來這裡的時候  她就一直在睡覺的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這是一般民宅不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現的話會被告違法入侵民宅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是不會醒的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！那是夢境之門哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的到處都是鐘錶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你的夢裡到處都是小汽車是一樣的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人的內心世界是一片黑暗加上壞損的鐘錶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！是鴿子時鐘啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！發現蒼星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  給我站住的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然逃得那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就進去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點醒一醒的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你如果想叫醒她應該用更溫和的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  還有真紅你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  蒼星石  你的琅碧卡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找的東西是這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善待老人家果然是有好報的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福  我兩三下就弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是用什麼卑鄙手段潛入這裡的說啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭  打開夢境之門的人可是你心愛的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道老爺爺想把自己關在夢境裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把門打開的  沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石  你居然為那個糟老頭做到這種地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說主人的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在說夢話的說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再把你打醒一次的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  光靠琅碧卡可能還稍嫌不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  翠星石  把你的水之夢也給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要太過份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把琅碧卡還來  水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不論在哪裡都一樣笨啊  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界  你認為你有勝算嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界是老爺爺的夢境世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對我非常好喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛也去幫忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  水銀燈交給我們應付
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著純與蒼星石離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  知道了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢境之門…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來主人不打算讓我們逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這裡的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就儘管掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好大  這就是老爺爺的樹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在看哪裡的說？這是樹枝  世界樹的樹枝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹枝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的夢都經由樹枝通往一棵巨大的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和世界樹連結在一起的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢和夢絕對不會混雜在一起的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是若受到世界樹樹枝的干涉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  請用30個字以內說明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  看來只好配合小不點的智能等級說明的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這根樹枝連繫著心意相通之人的夢境的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意相通？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的連繫正在逐漸枯萎的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的過得去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼難的  薔薇人偶的重量根本沒問題的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進入夢的世界了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為內心已經空蕩蕩了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個很悲傷的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的獨生子一樹  因為車禍過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此  主人的太太一直昏睡不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—定是太太的樹出了什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要解救這棵樹  老奶奶應該能從長眠中醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺不肯放你走  是因為太過孤單寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救老奶奶  就等於解救老爺爺的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要把你的心思朗讀出來不可的說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個不善言詞的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…翠星石  我希望你找到新的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過著幸福快樂的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然來到這裡只能放手一搏的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分頭去找老奶奶的樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類  你快去聞一聞臭味在哪裡的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是找松露的豬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去找樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說她不想醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼的說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個世界有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡什麼都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有可怕的車子  也沒有悲傷的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說  她要在這個安靜的世界永遠和我一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不用怕被人傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老爺爺該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去你之後他們想必也受到很大的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  因此逃離現實把自己關在安全的夢境世界裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己關在…安全的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸也是很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓她回去現實世界才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑  別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅他們怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  現在先逃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  人類你也飛起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  一樹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點把夢境之門關起來  不然水銀燈會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你們好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅跟雛莓怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道  可能在夢的世界裡迷路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用  沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有主人的你只能在夢的世界發揮力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況被奪走琅碧卡的人偶  只算是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的交出水之夢吧  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是不想動粗的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  只不過是幾根羽毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手的說  快點離開那裡的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒落魄到需要人類來救我的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點退下  要不然人類你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:17:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有落魄到放著軟弱無力的你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能硬撐到什麼時候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類  不行的說  快逃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琅碧卡已經是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用的  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應把水之夢給你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不要再傷害純了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  住手  翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是庫庫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫庫  庫庫  庫庫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你們出口在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  庫庫說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  請你們轉告我爸爸媽媽好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說不論在哪裡  我都會一直和他們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹  你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  連水之夢都被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不過  幸好大家都平安無事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡嗎  一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…你好  初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來搶我的一樹嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…才…才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想要這麼多麻煩的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的努波波人偶  現在買一送一大特價是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就說是賣兩隻不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種隨便敷衍的服務  我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然從背後偷襲  你這個壞心眼人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  是小雛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  那傢伙已經不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想她嗎？純
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰想她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了「一隻」囉嗦的傢伙  我才樂得清閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  奶奶  喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再幫我倒一杯好嗎  蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶碗給我一下  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣茶的溫度就會涼一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這點小事…我都不知道的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們大家都來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡當作自己家  放輕鬆點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  我會賜給你服侍主人的光榮機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快去泡紅茶  順便也準備些點心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛  怎麼突然大家都跑來了  我可是什麼都沒聽說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:24:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一切都因為事出突然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這只薔薇戒指發誓吧
